graph LR
    CodeFlare[CodeFlare Operator]

    %% External Dependencies (Required)
    CodeFlare -->|embeds v1.39.0| MCAD[Multi-Cluster App Dispatcher<br/>MCAD v1.39.0<br/>Queue-based scheduling]
    CodeFlare -->|framework| ControllerRuntime[controller-runtime v0.15.3<br/>Kubernetes controller framework]
    CodeFlare -->|API calls| K8sAPI[Kubernetes API Server<br/>v1.27.8<br/>Cluster control plane]

    %% External Dependencies (Optional)
    CodeFlare -.->|embeds v0.4.0<br/>optional| InstaScale[InstaScale v0.4.0<br/>Cluster autoscaling<br/>OpenShift Only]
    CodeFlare -.->|integrates<br/>optional| KubeRayExt[KubeRay v1.0.0<br/>External Ray cluster management]

    %% Internal RHOAI Dependencies
    CodeFlare -->|creates CRs| KubeRay[KubeRay Operator<br/>Manages Ray clusters]
    CodeFlare -->|metrics scraping| Prometheus[Prometheus<br/>Monitoring & alerting]
    CodeFlare -.->|API calls<br/>OpenShift only| MachineAPI[OpenShift Machine API<br/>Node provisioning]

    %% CRDs Managed
    MCAD -->|watches/manages| AppWrapper[AppWrapper CR<br/>workload.codeflare.dev/v1beta1]
    MCAD -->|watches/manages| SchedulingSpec[SchedulingSpec CR<br/>workload.codeflare.dev/v1beta1]
    CodeFlare -->|watches/manages| QuotaSubtree[QuotaSubtree CR<br/>quota.codeflare.dev/v1alpha1]
    MCAD -->|creates| RayCluster[RayCluster CR<br/>ray.io]

    %% Integration Points
    KubeRay -->|watches| RayCluster
    KubeRay -->|creates| RayPods[Ray Head/Worker Pods]
    InstaScale -->|creates/deletes| MachineSet[MachineSet CR<br/>machine.openshift.io]
    MachineAPI -->|provisions| CloudProvider[Cloud Provider API<br/>AWS/GCP/Azure]

    %% Prometheus Integration
    Prometheus -->|scrapes via ServiceMonitor| CodeFlare

